## Force change phone

```shell
curl -d "shop_id=SHOPID&shop_secret=SHOP_SECRET&new_phone=NEW_PHONE&old_phone=OLD_PHONE" https://<%= config[:api_endpoint] %>/profile/force_change_phone
```

